| Strong understanding of data structures and algorithms.             |\",\n    \"| Problem Solving         | 78                 | Able to solve complex problems with guidance.                   |\",\n    \"| Code Quality            | 92                 | Wrote clean and maintainable code.                               |\",\n    \"| Communication           | 88                 | Communicated effectively and clearly.                             |\",\n    \"| Cultural Fit & Behavior | 90                 | Demonstrated a positive attitude and willingness to learn.        |\",\n    \"\",\n    \"## 4. Strengths\",\n    \"- Proficient in Java and Python\",\n    \"- Strong understanding of data structures and algorithms\",\n    \"- AWS Certified Developer\",\n    \"\",\n    \"## 5. Areas for Improvement\",\n    \"- Needs more experience with cloud platforms (Azure, GCP)\",\n    \"- Needs more experience with machine learning principles\",\n    \"\",\n    \"## 6. Overall Recommendation\",\n    \"Recommended for a second interview. The candidate possesses the required skills and experience for the Software Engineer position.\"\n]\n```"}
